":264660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:46:19.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔到<br />\n組<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"070ad496238e6e3950842f0eaf90fb3009cb30d9","tid":1490142,"uid":112643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:17:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得如果係巡邏可以唔洗上曬所有裝備（如果係避免刀手而唔係警察啲tg）<br />\n我建議要著👷🏻&zwj;♀️👷🏻&zwj;♀️👷🏻&zwj;♀️（帶頭盔先lol）：<br />\n- blackbloc<br />\n- 帽/ 頭盔<br />\n- 面罩/口罩（費時咁容易比人認出）<br />\n- 手套<br />\n- 長遮<br />\n- 噴霧（不過唔知法律上用唔用得）<br />\n- 護掙護膝<br />\n- 急救用品（first-aider）<br />\n<br />\n隨身袋住：<br />\n- 豬嘴<br />\n- 頭盔<br />\n- 眼罩<br />\n- 雨嬲<br />\n<br />\n每個小隊3-5人不等，最好有齊：<br />\n- 大隻佬（坦）<br />\n- Medic （firstaider）<br />\n- 通訊 （save低記者同法援資料+報告現場情況）<br />\n<br />\n大致Duties：<br />\n1. 當自己區有放映會時，約五分鐘前帶定gear到現場集合。<br />\n2. 當放映會開始後，上裝備，3-5人為一小隊（小隊最好有齊勇武、medic、通訊），分批巡邏附近場所，觀察並報告現場情況。<br />\n3. 如遇突發情況，視乎嚴重性，由現場手足判斷行動。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n十八區group：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JpdlWxUVp6dzxVdPHompvg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJpdlWxUVp6dzxVdPHompvg&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VuaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=ea1a65a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JpdlWxUVp6dzxVdPHompvg</a><br />\n<br />\n東區group：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JpdlWxZ61Zx9zElSO7wD3g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJpdlWxZ61Zx9zElSO7wD3g&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VuaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=455747d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JpdlWxZ61Zx9zElSO7wD3g</a><br />\n<br />\n我都係第一次搞民衛，有咩裝備需要/唔需要、有咩做得唔好記得出聲，我可以改🙏🏻"},{"pid":"2a2dca54de068501566edb135f3f4435b3a11fa6","tid":1490142,"uid":112643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:18:06.000Z","msg":"推"}]}